#Connect$Connect
    This section is used to make calls to remote systems via the modem. It can be set up with the names and numbers of 42 remote systems. There must be an entry in the "System List" for the onsite system. Calls can be made by moving the cursor to the desired system and pressing the "INS" key. (mouse or keyboard)

 System List setup fields: 

1) Sys_name     Name of the system. 

2) Phone_no     Systems modem number. 

3) Directory    The field needed to access and save programs while on line to a system via a modem. 

4) Menu_file    The Menu File to be auto-loaded when calling that particular system. 

5) Baud_rate    The Baud Rate the remote panels modem is set at. 
 
6) Link_no      If YES the phone number continues on to the next line down.
