#Programs$Programs
    Control Basic is the programming language of the T3000. To access an individual program press the "Ins" key while highlighting that program.
    Control Basic setup fields: 
a)  Full_label      
    A 20 character descriptor of the point. 

b)  Status
    Indicates whether the program is running or not (ON/OFF). 

c)  A/m
